### [Gist Previewer](https://davidyorr.github.io/gist-previewer)
Chrome extension that renders Gist repos that contain HTML, JavaScript, or CSS files.

### [MangoDocs](https://davidyorr.github.io/mangodocs)
Documentation generator for JavaScript files.
